LORE serathi
FLAGS SERATHI
Avian humanoids of the western sky-roads; plumage: deep brown-and-gold
(desert hawk), grey-white (high altitude), iridescent storm-black (coastal)
Orient by sky-lines: horizon profiles of ridges and canopies readable only
from above; every adult has their home territory memorized to altitude-
identification precision
Direct and honest to a fault; surface-bound evasion is genuinely difficult
for them; the sky does not lie; they find face-saving strange
"Roc Road" named for the roc mythology Serathi presence created; travelers
reporting enormous winged shapes in mountain pass skies were mostly seeing
Serathi hunting parties at altitude
Sky-line records of western passes predate any Keeper survey document; Kiess
Trade Syndics want access to their chronicles of Evermeet's collapse
Talons map to HOOVES equipment slot; standard boots do not fit; talon-clasp
guards and wrapped talon-braces are the relevant equipment type
~
